(firstQuint)Balanced Volume Replacement Therapy With Ringer's Acetate Solution in Burn Injury.

 In the early period following severe burn injury volume replacement with high amounts of crystalloids is necessary.

 In this study we compare the organ function scores of a historical patient group, treated with Ringer's Lactate solution, with an actual patient population, treated with Ringer's Acetate solution.

